headline: Molina Healthcare Awarded Contracts to Serve Dual Eligible Populations in Michigan and Idaho
summary: LONG BEACH, Calif., December 16, 2024--Molina Healthcare, Inc. (NYSE: MOH) ("Molina" or the "Company") announced today that the Michigan Department of Health and Human Services (MDHHS) has awarded a contract to Molina’s health plan subsidiary, Molina Healthcare of Michigan, to provide a Highly Integrated Dual Eligible Special Needs Plan (HIDE SNP). This new award follows the initial notice of intent to award the HIDE SNP contract announced by the MDHHS on October 9, 2024, and subsequently cancel
